    <abstract>
      <t>This document is a glossary of policy-related terms.  It provides abbreviations, explanations, and recommendations for use of these terms.  The intent is to improve the comprehensibility and consistency of writing that deals with network policy, particularly Internet Standards documents (ISDs).  This memo provides information for the Internet community.
	 </t>
